      "px930101_protective_equiptment_survey_last_five_days_close_contact_risk_group_covid19": "Thinking about your current social habits, in the last 5 days: I have been in close contact with someone who is in a risk group for COVID-19 (adults age 50+, people with chronic medical conditions like heart, lung, liver, or kidney disease, diabetes, high blood pressure, or a suppressed immune system). This includes someone inside or outside of your household.",
